===================================================================
REGISTRATION CONFIRMATION
===================================================================

<%= @registration.event.name %> | <%= relative_date_span [@registration.event.start_date, @registration.event.end_date] %> | <%= @registration.event.location %>

<%= @registration.event.description %>

View more event details or register more attendees at: http://register.prosperitypartnership.org/event/<%= @registration.event.id %>

Registration confirmation #: <%= @registration.id %>

Payment method: <%= @registration.payment.payment_method %>

<% unless @registration.invoiceable? %>
===================================================================
INVOICE
===================================================================

Please mail your payment of <%= number_to_currency @registration.event_option.price %> with a copy of this invoice to:
    
Puget Sound Regional Council
1011 Western Ave, Suite 500
Seattle, WA 98104
<% else %>
===================================================================
PAYMENT INFORMATION
===================================================================

Note, this is not an invoice.  Your credit card was successfully charged <%= number_to_currency @registration.event_option.price %>.
<% end %>
For all billing questions, please contact Andrew Werfelmann at 206-971-3292 or awerfelmann@psrc.org

===================================================================
REGISTERED ATTENDEES (<%= @registration.registration_set.attendees.size %>)
===================================================================
<% for person in @registration.registration_set.attendees %><% next if person.blank? %>
<%= person.name %> (<%= person.email %>) <%= (person.vegetarian == "1") ? "(V)" : "" %>
Organization: <%= person.organization %> <%= "| Table: #{ @registration.registration_set.table_name }" unless @registration.registration_set.table_name.blank? %>
<% end %>
